<item>
            <title>[SOLR-7108] Change PingRequestHandler hard-coded troublesome query</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7108</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;PingRequestHandler hard-codes this:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;ping.initArgs.add(INVARIANTS, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; NamedList&amp;lt;&amp;gt;(makeMap(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;echoParams&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;all&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;q&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;solrpingquery&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)));
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;which unnecessarily relies on query parsing settings like default field.  In the case of the basic_configs core this causes a failed request because df isn&apos;t set appropriately).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
