                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14320203" author="ehatcher" created="Fri, 13 Feb 2015 15:02:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Let&apos;s switch the query to something like&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;{!lucene}*:*
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;so that it will always parse and execute correctly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14562316" author="mariusneo" created="Thu, 28 May 2015 05:35:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached is a patch for the reported issue containing changes in the configuration files, ImplicitPlugins.java as well as unit tests for accuracy and failure of the PingRequestHandler.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I had a look on how the ping requests are handled and discovered within the QueryComponent line 144&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; defType = params.get(QueryParsing.DEFTYPE, QParserPlugin.DEFAULT_QTYPE);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;that the default query parser is the lucene parser &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;QParserPlugin.DEFAULT_QTYPE = lucene&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt; reason why the hint &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;{!lucene}*:*&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;that the Lucene query parser should be used is not necessary. This is why I used &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;*:*&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt; query parameter value.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14576412" author="jira-bot" created="Sun, 7 Jun 2015 20:03:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1684071 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ehatcher&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ehatcher&quot;&gt;ehatcher&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;dev/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1684071&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1684071&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7108&quot; title=&quot;Change PingRequestHandler hard-coded troublesome query&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-7108&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-7108&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Change default query used by /admin/ping to not rely on other parameters such as query parser or default field&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14576413" author="jira-bot" created="Sun, 7 Jun 2015 20:05:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1684073 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ehatcher&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ehatcher&quot;&gt;ehatcher&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;dev/branches/branch_5x&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1684073&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1684073&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7108&quot; title=&quot;Change PingRequestHandler hard-coded troublesome query&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-7108&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-7108&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Change default query used by /admin/ping to not rely on other parameters such as query parser or default field (merged from trunk r1684071)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14576417" author="ehatcher" created="Sun, 7 Jun 2015 20:09:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;resolved.  &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=marius_neo&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;marius_neo&quot;&gt;marius_neo&lt;/a&gt; - The query parser is needed to be entirely sure because /admin/ping will use a select handler (defaults /select) to execute the query which could specify defType and cause issues; better safe(r) than sorry.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14576420" author="ehatcher" created="Sun, 7 Jun 2015 20:11:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In addition, perhaps all those /admin/ping&apos;s explicitly defined should be removed so the default/implicit configuration is used. - spun off &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7645&quot; title=&quot;Remove explicitly defined plugins that are now implicitly available&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-7645&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-7645&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for this broader than ping cleanup task.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14713261" author="shalinmangar" created="Wed, 26 Aug 2015 13:06:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Bulk close for 5.3.0 release&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
